column2: SELECT   p.modelMag_u as m_u,   p.modelMag_g as m_g,   p.modelMag_r as m_r,   p.modelMag_i as m_i,   p.modelMag_z as m_z,      p.petroMag_u as pm_u,   p.petroMag_g as pm_g,   p.petroMag_r as pm_r,   p.petroMag_i as pm_i,   p.petroMag_z as pm_z,      p.modelMag_u-p.extinction_u-p.modelMag_g+p.extinction_g as ug,   p.modelMag_g-p.extinction_g-p.modelMag_r+p.extinction_r as gr,   p.modelMag_r-p.extinction_r-p.modelMag_i+p.extinction_i as ri,   p.modelMag_i-p.extinction_i-p.modelMag_z+p.extinction_z as ug,         ...   p.modelMag_i-p.extinction_i-p.modelMag_z+p.extinction_z as iz,   p.petroMag_u-p.extinction_u-p.petroMag_g+p.extinction_g as p_ug,   ...   p.petroMag_i-p.extinction_i-p.petroMag_z+p.extinction_z as p_iz,   s.z as z into mydb.MyTable from PhotoObj AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.probPSF=# AND   p.petroMagErr_u/p.petroMag_u BETWEEN # AND # AND   ...   p.modelMagErr_z/p.modelMag_z BETWEEN # AND #
